## Verification Plan

### Browser Testing

1. Run `npm run dev` and open `http://localhost:3000` in the browser.
2. Verify hero video plays, text animates, stat counters animate on scroll.
3. Scroll through all sections — confirm fade-in animations trigger.
4. Resize browser to mobile width — confirm hamburger menu works, layout stacks.
5. Click nav links — confirm smooth scroll to each section.
6. Test contact form validation (empty submit should show errors).
7. Confirm footer renders correctly with all columns.

### Build Verification

```bash
npm run build
```

Confirm zero build errors.
